* D whined and kept struggling, not liking the feeling of his feet not being 
on the ground. He looked up at Fenox and stopped struggling the second she 
said that he might drop if he didn't.
He wasn't about to drop. But it was pretty frightning to suddenly wake up in 
the air after being in a ship the last moment.
D didn't move a muscle and kept his ears plastered against his skull, he 
hated this!*
